import {
  Box,
  Center,
  IconButton,
  Text,
  Flex,
  Input,
  Icon,
  HStack,
  Avatar,
} from "@chakra-ui/react"
import { ChevronRightIcon } from "@chakra-ui/icons"
import { RiSearchLine, RiNotificationLine, RiUserAddLine } from "react-icons/ri"

const Header = () => (
  <Flex
    w="100%"
    as="header"
    maxWidth={1480}
    h="20"
    mx="auto"
    mt="4"
    align="center"
  >
    <Flex align="center" ml="auto">
      <HStack
        mx="8"
        pr="8"
        py="1"
        spacing="8"
        color="gray.300"
        borderRightWidth={1}
        borderColor="gray.700"
      >
        <Icon as={RiNotificationLine} fontSize="20" />
      </HStack>
      <Flex align="center">
        <Box mr="4" textAlign="right">
          <Text>Victor Mesquita</Text>
          <Text color="gray.300" fontSize="small">
            mesquitadev@gmail.com
          </Text>
        </Box>
        <Avatar size="md" name="Victor Mesquita" />
      </Flex>
    </Flex>
  </Flex>
)

export default Header
